title: Top Floor Junior 1 Bedroom in Remodeled Landmark Victorian
posting_body: ['Contact Information', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Bianca', 'Call today to schedule a showing!', 'A note from the Owner', 'Owner is looking for excellent credit, income 3x the monthly rent and no dogs.', 'Tenants pay all utilities.', 'Security Deposit is 1.5x the monthly rent.', 'Property Details', 'Price: $2850', 'Bedrooms: Junior 1 Bedroom', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Sq Ft: 456', 'Description', '1050 Dolores St. Apt.', 'B $2850', 'Top Floor.', 'Junior 1 Bedroom 1 bath.', 'High ceilings.', 'Hardwood floors throughout.', 'Remodeled kitchen with cherrywood cabinets, granite counters and stainless steel appliances.', 'Beautiful tile and marble bath.', 'Unit is drenched in light.', 'Original Carrara marble fireplace with gas insert.', "2 blocks to Bart/Muni(J-Church line)--1 Block to 24th Street shopping with local restaurants, WHOLE FOODS MARKET, boutiques and coffee shops(La Boulange and Martha's Coffee)--Easy freeway access to 280 and 101.", 'Parking available ($175/ month)', 'Laundry-use of laundry room in owners building next door.', 'Sorry no dogs allowed.', 'This building has been remodeled/restored from the foundation to the roof with attention to every victorian detail thruout.', 'Each unit has an Alarm System paid for by owner.', 'Unit will be delivered unfurnished.', 'FEATURES:- Great Location!- TOP FLOOR!', '- Fireplace - Shower over Bathtub', 'Amenities', "-96 Walk Score: Walker's Paradise, daily errands do not require a car", '-75 Bike Score: Very Bikeable, biking is convenient for most trips', '-23 minutes to Downtown via public transport', '-5 minute walk to Noe Valley shops and restaurants', '-5 minute walk to Dolores Park', 'Powered by TourVista']
